<h1>Attributes are Property + Value</h1>

<a href="https://wwww.website.com">Text that shows as link</a>
<!-- a = anchor tag, create links to other pages
defaults to file protocol, if www.google.com will go to Desktop/www.google.com, need https://!!-->
<a href="page2">Click to go to page 2</a>
<!-- page2 is a html file he created, same directory as firstpage.html so will open it up bc relative path -->

<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/master.css">

<img src="url of photo or dog.jpg if same directory" alt="">
<!-- src=source very common attribute for files -->

